room_title: Escape room "Fallout Shelter" by 11th Hour Escape in Austin
room_description:
It's the end of the world. Locked in a fallout shelter, there are plenty of supplies to last you and your group awhile. But that's where the good news end... You discover a problem with the oxygen supply and realize you must escape the shelter in 60 minutes.
Your group can choose the level of difficulty: easy (50% success rate), medium (25%) or hard (10%).
